  "text": "Who am I here with today? My name is Dr. Shaquille O'Neal. What industry did you decide to pursue a career in? A lot of them. What were you doing prior to becoming a business mogul? What was I doing, Brian? Yeah. I was killing your favorite NBA player. Let me ask you this. You became one of the greatest athletes of all time. What was the biggest driving factor of success for you throughout your career? I was a thief. Let me explain. If you see somebody that's doing better than you, steal what they're doing. So for me, I stole Michael Jordan. I stole Karima Dujebaugh. I stole Mahal Manali. And I put it inside my brain and I created me. Shaquille O'Neal. And you generated and made hundreds of millions of dollars throughout your career. There's a stat sports illustrator just did that. One in three NFL players go broke within three to five years. What's the best way to preserve that kind of wealth? I think for those who are not financial literate, learn this word, annuity. You own 155 guys at one point. I sold them. You sold them? Yeah, I sold them. What's your secret to scaling in the franchise model? Just businesses in general. The secret to scaling is one word, delegation. I can't be in 155 places every month, but I know somebody that can. So you're really good at bringing other people in to run these businesses. Yes, I am. And among yourself and the most highly successful people that you study and know, what is that one trait they all have in common? They keep it very simple. Like Jeff Bezos said, you invest in things that's going to change people's lives. I heard him say that and I changed my home investment strategy and I've been very interested. What's the number one thing that you look for people when you're investing in a business? I like to believe in what they believe in. Like for example, if you was going to start this company and you came in with those beautiful eyes and you told me you're passionate, I would definitely invest in you. I'm a big fan of yours. You're an amazing advice, my friend. I really appreciate you. He's a lot. I gotta come over here. Thank you.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.0,
      "text": "Who am I here with today?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.2,
      "end": 2.5,
      "text": "My name is Dr. Shaquille O'Neal."
    },
    {
      "start": 2.7,
      "end": 4.7,
      "text": "What industry did you decide to pursue a career in?"
    },
    {
      "start": 4.8,
      "end": 5.4,
      "text": "A lot of them."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.4,
      "end": 7.2,
      "text": "What were you doing prior to becoming a business mogul?"
    },
    {
      "start": 7.3,
      "end": 7.9,
      "text": "What was I doing, Brian?"
    },
    {
      "start": 8.1,
      "end": 8.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 8.3,
      "end": 9.9,
      "text": "I was killing your favorite NBA player."
    },
    {
      "start": 10.1,
      "end": 10.5,
      "text": "Let me ask you this."
    },
    {
      "start": 10.6,
      "end": 12.6,
      "text": "You became one of the greatest athletes of all time."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.7,
      "end": 14.6,
      "text": "What was the biggest driving factor of success"
    },
    {
      "start": 14.6,
      "end": 15.7,
      "text": "for you throughout your career?"
    },
    {
      "start": 15.8,
      "end": 16.4,
      "text": "I was a thief."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.7,
      "end": 17.3,
      "text": "Let me explain."
    },
    {
      "start": 17.5,
      "end": 19.4,
      "text": "If you see somebody that's doing better than you,"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.6,
      "end": 20.6,
      "text": "steal what they're doing."
    },
    {
      "start": 20.8,
      "end": 22.5,
      "text": "So for me, I stole Michael Jordan."
    },
    {
      "start": 22.6,
      "end": 24.0,
      "text": "I stole Karima Dujebaugh."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.1,
      "end": 25.1,
      "text": "I stole Mahal Manali."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.5,
      "end": 27.8,
      "text": "And I put it inside my brain and I created me."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.0,
      "end": 28.6,
      "text": "Shaquille O'Neal."
    },
    {
      "start": 28.6,
      "end": 31.2,
      "text": "And you generated and made hundreds of millions of dollars"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.2,
      "end": 32.1,
      "text": "throughout your career."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.3,
      "end": 34.1,
      "text": "There's a stat sports illustrator just did that."
    },
    {
      "start": 34.3,
      "end": 37.2,
      "text": "One in three NFL players go broke within three to five years."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.4,
      "end": 39.2,
      "text": "What's the best way to preserve that kind of wealth?"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.4,
      "end": 41.8,
      "text": "I think for those who are not financial literate,"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.9,
      "end": 43.2,
      "text": "learn this word, annuity."
    },
    {
      "start": 43.5,
      "end": 45.6,
      "text": "You own 155 guys at one point."
    },
    {
      "start": 45.8,
      "end": 46.2,
      "text": "I sold them."
    },
    {
      "start": 46.3,
      "end": 46.7,
      "text": "You sold them?"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.8,
      "end": 47.3,
      "text": "Yeah, I sold them."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.4,
      "end": 49.3,
      "text": "What's your secret to scaling in the franchise model?"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.5,
      "end": 50.4,
      "text": "Just businesses in general."
    },
    {
      "start": 50.5,
      "end": 52.6,
      "text": "The secret to scaling is one word, delegation."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.8,
      "end": 54.9,
      "text": "I can't be in 155 places every month,"
    },
    {
      "start": 54.9,
      "end": 56.5,
      "text": "but I know somebody that can."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.9,
      "end": 59.6,
      "text": "So you're really good at bringing other people in"
    },
    {
      "start": 59.6,
      "end": 60.2,
      "text": "to run these businesses."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.4,
      "end": 60.8,
      "text": "Yes, I am."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.9,
      "end": 62.9,
      "text": "And among yourself and the most highly successful people"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.9,
      "end": 64.7,
      "text": "that you study and know, what is that one trait"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.7,
      "end": 65.6,
      "text": "they all have in common?"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.6,
      "end": 66.6,
      "text": "They keep it very simple."
    },
    {
      "start": 66.9,
      "end": 68.7,
      "text": "Like Jeff Bezos said, you invest in things"
    },
    {
      "start": 68.7,
      "end": 70.0,
      "text": "that's going to change people's lives."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.2,
      "end": 72.3,
      "text": "I heard him say that and I changed my home investment"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.3,
      "end": 73.7,
      "text": "strategy and I've been very interested."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.2,
      "end": 75.5,
      "text": "What's the number one thing that you look for people"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.5,
      "end": 76.4,
      "text": "when you're investing in a business?"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.7,
      "end": 78.2,
      "text": "I like to believe in what they believe in."
    },
    {
      "start": 78.4,
      "end": 80.2,
      "text": "Like for example, if you was going to start this company"
    },
    {
      "start": 80.2,
      "end": 81.8,
      "text": "and you came in with those beautiful eyes"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.8,
      "end": 82.9,
      "text": "and you told me you're passionate,"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.1,
      "end": 84.2,
      "text": "I would definitely invest in you."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.3,
      "end": 85.3,
      "text": "I'm a big fan of yours."
    },
    {
      "start": 85.3,
      "end": 86.6,
      "text": "You're an amazing advice, my friend."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.0,
      "end": 87.8,
      "text": "I really appreciate you."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.8,
      "end": 88.3,
      "text": "He's a lot."
    },
    {
      "start": 88.4,
      "end": 89.2,
      "text": "I gotta come over here."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.3,
      "end": 89.6,
      "text": "Thank you."
    }
  ],
